{"_id":"Vy8vl2mJyaeZ9s6W","name":"Dark Ego - I Will Have My Satisfaction","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>cuando eliges a un oponente, ya no tiene escapatoria. Una vez por escena, puedes realizar una acción adicional contra el objetivo de tu desafío (incluso si ya habías actuado durante este intercambio) para anticiparte a su movimiento y detener su acción con la tuya. Si un oponente te inflige una Herida, disfrutas del sabor del desafío y obtienes 1 Éxito adicional en las pruebas que realices contra ese oponente durante el resto de la escena.</p>","trigger":"desafías a un enemigo o dejas claro de algún otro modo quién eres y el nivel de tus habilidades."},"name":"Ego oscuro – Tendré mi recompensa"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Associated Descriptor</h3>I am a man of the world and nothing can really surprise me anymore. I never question myself. After all, I’m the best at what I do.<h3>Dark Ego</h3>When you choose an opponent, there is no escape for them. Once per Scene, you can take an additional action against the target of your challenge (even if you had already acted during this Exchange) to anticipate their move and stop their action with yours. If an opponent inflicts a Wound on you, you savor the taste of the challenge and receive 1 Additional Success at each Check against them for the rest of the Scenario.","notes":"James the Swordsman - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"You challenge an enemy or otherwise make clear who and how skilled you are."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241691,"modifiedTime":1783973241691,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"VRrgMVpuB99iKBAa","name":"Dark Ego - The Big Bad Wolf","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>llevas toda una vida en las grandes montañas y tu destreza solo es comparable a tu valentía. Cuando desates tu furia, crea un descriptor para ella que incluya al menos una de estas palabras: Fuerte, Feroz, Imparable. Puedes emplear la fuerza de tres hombres, roer la piedra con la misma facilidad que la carne o derribar cualquier barrera. Cuando actúas usando este descriptor especial para pruebas de posición, obtienes 1 Éxito adicional. Una vez por escena, puedes desatar tu furia y obtener 3 Éxitos adicionales en lugar de 1.</p>","trigger":"adoptas la forma de un lobo o te revelas como lo que realmente eres, asustando a los humanos débiles."},"name":"Ego oscuro - El gran lobo feroz"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Associated Descriptor</h3>I am fiercer and more powerful than any human and my fangs can pierce even metal. My proud wolf spirit is everything to me.<h3>Dark Ego</h3>You are hardened by a lifetime in the great mountains and your skill is matched only by your courage. When you unleash your rage, create a Descriptor for it that includes at least one of these words: Strong, Fierce, Unstoppable. You can employ the strength of three men, gnaw through stone as easily as flesh, or break down any barrier. When you act using this special Descriptor for Position Checks, you get 1 Additional Success. Once per Scene, you can unleash your rage and receive 3 Additional Successes instead of 1.","notes":"Garou the Old Wolf - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"You assume the form of a Wolf or reveal yourself for what you really are, scaring off weak humans."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241691,"modifiedTime":1783973241691,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"59gVW5SM6kTbuaG0","name":"Dark Ego - The Power of Music","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>una vez por escena, puedes emitir un sonido que puede percibe quien tú quieras, incluso a gran distancia. Todo el que lo oye sufre 1 Herida, los objetos frágiles se rompen y los animales asustados huyen. Alternativamente, puedes tocar una suave melodía y el propio viento te obedecerá, llevando tu mensaje a quien tú quieras, esté donde esté. Al usar El poder de la música, también puedes activar un efecto de Música del alma en uno o más objetivos de tu elección.</p>","trigger":"demostrar tu arte en toda su extensión, con un espectáculo que no se puede pasar por alto."},"name":"Ego oscuro – El poder de la música"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Associated Descriptor</h3>As an artist I have traveled to many places and I know many myths and legends. I’m hungry for knowledge and I’m fascinated by everything I don’t know.<h3>Dark Ego</h3>Once per Scene, you can make a sound that can be heard by whomever you wish, even from a great distance. Everyone who hears it suffers 1 Wound, fragile objects break, and frightened animals flee. Alternatively, you can play a gentle melody and the wind itself will obey you, carrying your message to whomever you wish, wherever they are. When using The Power of Music, you can also activate a Soul Music effect on one or more targets of your choice.","notes":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Demonstrate your art to its fullest extent, with a show that cannot be ignored."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241691,"modifiedTime":1783973241691,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"1BSPSTCB2YO9EqEq","name":"Dark Ego - The Evil Witch","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>obtienes 1 Éxito adicional en cualquier prueba cuando utilices uno de tus hechizos, ya sea a través del don Magia o introduciéndolo en tu narración a través de los descriptores. Además, puedes desatar tu aura maligna para obtener uno o más de los siguientes efectos: 1. Los animales y la gente corriente se sienten atormentados por tu presencia y huirán despavoridos. 2. Obtienes 1 Éxito adicional si utilizas tu magia para castigar a alguien por romper una promesa o un acuerdo alcanzado anteriormente. 3. En el área que te rodea, puedes convocar la luz del día o la oscuridad.</p>","trigger":"Asustar a la gente corriente o imponer castigos a través de tu magia."},"name":"Ego oscuro - La bruja malvada"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Associated Descriptor</h3>Like any respectable sorceress, I carry my trusty bag full of herbs, poisons, and all kinds of magic tools. My childlike appearance is often useful, but sometimes it leads others to underestimate me. I hate that.<h3>Dark Ego</h3>Receive 1 Additional Success on any Check when you use one of your spells, either through the Magic Gift or by inserting it into your narrative through the Descriptors. Moreover, you can unleash your evil aura to gain one or more of the following effects:\n1. Animals and ordinary people are tormented by your presence and will flee in terror.\n2. You gain 1 Additional Success if you use your magic to punish someone for breaking a promise or agreement you made earlier.\n3. In the area around you, you can summon daylight or darkness.","notes":"Baba yaga The Child Witch - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Scare ordinary people or dispense punishment through your magic."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241691,"modifiedTime":1783973241691,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"lxVBw4oloH2FBLs4","name":"Dark Ego - As I Want!","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>sabes que tu camino es el único correcto para hacer las cosas. Durante la escena, como acción adicional, puedes elegir a otro personaje al que le darás una orden. En el caso de un aliado, si hace exactamente lo que le dices, recibirá 1 Éxito adicional para su acción o aumentará su Nivel de Oposición en 1. Si das una orden imperativa para atrapar a un enemigo, bajará su Nivel de Oposición en 1 o, si ya lo has visto en acción, puedes impedir que use uno de sus dones. Una vez por escena, puedes gritar, atrayendo la atención de todos hacia ti. Durante unos instantes, harán una pausa para escuchar lo que tienes que decir.</p>","trigger":"tomar el control de una situación e imponer tus decisiones llamando la atención de forma espectacular."},"name":"Ego oscuro - ¡Como yo lo mando!"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Associated Descriptor</h3>I have an enviable charm and love to dress up to fit the role I have chosen. Even when I try to restrain myself, I never go unnoticed.<h3>Dark Ego</h3>You know that your way is the only right way to do things. During the Scene, as an additional action, you can choose another character who will be issued a command. In the case of an ally, if they do exactly what you tell them, they will receive 1 Additional Success to their action or increase their Opposition Level by 1. If you give a peremptory order to ensnare an enemy, they will lower their Opposition Level by 1 or, if you’ve already seen it in action, you can prevent them from using one of their Gifts. Once per Scene, you can shout, drawing everyone’s attention to you. For a few moments, they will pause to listen to what you have to say.","notes":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Take control of a situation and impose your decisions by dramatically drawing attention to yourself."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241691,"modifiedTime":1783973241691,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"okLhO5Pi59LmOb7O","name":"Dark Ego - If you don’t Stop, I’ll Call the Bogeyman!","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>eres como una sombra serpenteante capaz de desplazarse a cualquier sitio. Durante una escena, puedes llegar a un lugar cubriendo cualquier distancia y superando cualquier obstáculo si uno de tus aliados o un PNJ te llama por tu nombre. Cuando manifiestes tu verdadera naturaleza, todos los que lo presencien se asustarán y no actuarán contra ti a menos que los amenaces primero. El Narrador puede pedirte una prueba de posición para asustar a personajes especialmente poderosos. Obtienes 1 Éxito adicional en todas las pruebas de defensa que hagas contra las acciones de alguien que esté asustado.</p>","trigger":"entra o sal de una sombra manifestando tu verdadera naturaleza y asustando a alguien."},"name":"Ego oscuro - ¡Si no paras, llamaré al hombre del saco"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Associated Descriptor</h3>My presence intimidates people, touching the fear that dwells deep in their hearts. The presence of children and their innocent way of looking at the world makes me uneasy.<h3>Dark Ego</h3>You are like a sinuous shadow that can reach anywhere. During a Scene, you can arrive at a location by covering any distance and overcoming any obstacle if one of your allies or an NPC calls your name. When you manifest your true nature, everyone who witnesses it will be frightened and will not act against you unless you threaten them first. The Storyteller may ask you for a Position Check to frighten particularly powerful characters. Receive 1 Additional Success on all Defense Checks you make against the actions of someone who is now fearful.","notes":"Babai the Judge - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Enter or leave a shadow by manifesting your true nature and scaring someone."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241692,"modifiedTime":1783973241692,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"2xU4KRIDjHUv5JaW","name":"Dark Ego - Soft and Succulent Flesh","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>la verdad es que ansías la carne humana, especialmente cruda y tomada de gente maligna. Cuando infliges una Herida mediante una acción violenta a alguien que consideras maligno, y si consigues un triunfo con un Incremento, puedes infligir 1 Herida adicional. Una vez por escena, cuando consumes carne humana, recuperas 1 Herida y el Narrador revelará algunos recuerdos de la víctima, dándote información contextualizada sobre lo que estás buscando.</p>","trigger":"manifiestas descaradamente tu deseo de devorar carne humana, sin que te importen las consecuencias."},"name":"Ego oscuro - Carne blanda y suculenta"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Associated Descriptor</h3>I love human flesh and can gain insight about people just looking at them. I am helplessly attracted to those who have a particular physical trait that stimulates my appetite, such as a good smell or velvety skin.<h3>Dark Ego</h3>The truth is that you crave human flesh, especially when raw and taken from evil people. When you inflict a Wound through violent action on someone you deem evil, and if you reach an Outcome with an Increment, you may inflict 1 additional Wound. Once per Scene when you consume human flesh, you recover 1 Wound and the Storyteller will reveal some memories of the victim, giving you contextualized information about what you are looking for.","notes":"The Woman from the Woods - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Blatantly manifest your desire to devour human flesh, regardless of the consequences."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241692,"modifiedTime":1783973241692,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Ke4XIrSMRgQiHycG","name":"Dark Ego - The Immortal","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>cuando sufres 1 Herida, puedes gastar inmediatamente 1 Soma para permanecer consciente, lo que te permite sufrir muchas</p>"},"name":"Ego oscuro - El Inmortal"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Associated Descriptor</h3>My body is but a tool which I can manipulate at will, far beyond common human limits. In spite of my old and emaciated appearance, I feel neither fatigue nor pain. With matters of the flesh no longer of concern, I value beautiful things and works of art above anything else.<h3>Dark Ego</h3>When you suffer 1 Wound, you can immediately spend 1 Soma to remain conscious, allowing you to suffer many Wounds without dying. You are in full control of your body, even parts that have been cut off. You can see through a torn eye or continue to use your severed hand. At the end of the Scene in which you activated your Dark Ego, you recover all Wounds suffered except the first one. Your body regenerates and severed parts reattach in a horrific spectacle.","notes":"TheImmortal - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Use your indifference to pain or death to your advantage, revealing your true nature for anyone to see."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241692,"modifiedTime":1783973241692,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"n7nOsNsHPxeE04dH","name":"Dark Ego - Treasures of the Sea","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>al principio del escenario, obtienes 2 Contadores de tesoro. Cuando muestres tus tesoros, gasta 1 Contador de tesoro y 1 Soma, y crea un descriptor que lo represente, como por ejemplo Daga matalobos o Lente de la verdad . Obtén 1 Éxito adicional en cualquier prueba en la que tu tesoro pueda ser útil. Alternativamente, gasta 1 Contador para sacar una Poción de tu bolsa y dársela a alguien. Crea un descriptor para representar su efecto mágico, por ejemplo Ver en la oscuridad o Fuerza extraordinaria. Quien la beba obtendrá el descriptor que has creado durante 1 escena, más 1 Éxito adicional en la primera acción en la que utilice la ventaja otorgada por la poción. Cuando obtengas un nuevo tesoro o cierres un trato favorable, recibirás 1 Contador de tesoro.</p>","trigger":"convertir una petición de ayuda o una conversación en una negociación, dejando claro lo increíbles que son tus tesoros."},"name":"Ego oscuro – Tesoros del mar"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Associated Descriptor</h3>I have a massive collection of magical relics and treasures. I am very stingy with my collection and constantly seeking to add to my wealth so I can redeem my freedom.<h3>Dark Ego</h3>At the beginning of the Scenario, you receive 2 Treasure Tokens. When you show off your Treasures, spend 1 Treasure Token and 1 Soma, and create a Descriptor that represents it such as Wolf-Slaying Dagger or Lens of Truth. Receive 1 Additional Success for any Check in which your Treasure may be helpful. Alternatively, spend 1 Token to draw a Potion from your pouch to give to someone. Create a Descriptor to represent its magical effect such as Seeing in the dark or Extraordinary strength. Whoever drinks it will be granted the Descriptor you created for 1 Scene, plus 1 Additional Success on the first action in which they use the advantage given by the potion. When you obtain a new treasure or close a favorable deal, you receive 1 Treasure Token.","notes":"Marina the Sea Explorer - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Turn a request for help or a conversation into a negotiation, making it clear how amazing your treasures are."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241692,"modifiedTime":1783973241692,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"YVpBR3Xwp7hPnaPN","name":"Dark Ego - The Demon Revealed","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>aunque generalmente mantienes el control, de vez en cuando tienes que permitir que el demonio se manifieste y desate su ira. Crea un descriptor que represente tu forma demoníaca y que incluya al menos una de estas palabras: Monstruoso, Feroz, Bestial. Tus características físicas van mucho más allá de las de un simple mortal, pero te comportarás como un demonio, disfrutando de la maldad y el miedo que inspiras. Cuando actúas usando este descriptor especial, obtienes 1 Éxito adicional. Puedes gastar 1 Contador de diablo para infligir 1 Herida adicional o para gastar como Soma en una prueba. Una vez por escenario, el Narrador puede usar 1 Contador de diablo para activar este don contra tu voluntad.</p>","trigger":"dar rienda suelta a tu lado demoníaco o escuchar el sonido de campanas o cencerros durante al menos un minuto."},"name":"Ego oscuro – El demonio revelado"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Associated Descriptor</h3>The demon in me grants me its power, allowing me to act with savage strength and speed. It is not easy to contain this ferocity and, often, I end up hurting or destroying things I did not wish to.<h3>Dark Ego</h3>While generally retaining control, every now and then you have to allow the demon to manifest and unleash its anger. Create a Descriptor that represents your demonic form and that includes at least one of these words: Monstrous, Fierce, Beastly. Your physical abilities go far beyond those of a mere mortal, but you will behave like a devil, enjoying the evil and fear you inspire. When you act using this special Descriptor, you gain 1 Additional Success. You can spend 1 Devil Token to inflict 1 additional Wound or to spend as Soma for a Check. Once per Scenario, the Storyteller can spend 1 Devil Token to activate this Gift against your will.","notes":"Niklaus von Krampus - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Give free rein to your demonic side or listen to the sound of bells or cowbells for at least one minute."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241692,"modifiedTime":1783973241692,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"WMWOfghoddbhq818","name":"Dark Ego - The Saint","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>cuando canalizas el poder divino sagrado, todo el mundo inclina la cabeza. La gente corriente te muestra reverencia, mientras que los PNJ enemigos más débiles (a discreción del Narrador) no te atacan a menos que seas la única opción disponible, ni intentan interponerse en tu camino. En tu presencia, cualquiera que tenga poderes relacionados con lo sobrenatural reduce su Nivel de Oposición en 1. Tu aura sagrada emite una luz intensa que puede iluminar toda la zona que te rodea a tu voluntad.</p>","trigger":"invocar el santo poder divino, reprendiendo a todos los pecadores y dando ejemplo de pureza y rectitud."},"name":"Ego oscuro – El santo"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Associated Descriptor</h3>I am a saint in the eyes of ordinary people and no door remains closed for me. My word is that of the Church itself. What I say is not to be questioned.<h3>Dark Ego</h3>When you channel sacred divine power, everyone bows their heads. Ordinary people will show you reverence, while weaker enemy NPCs (at the Storyteller’s discretion) won’t target you unless you’re the only available option, nor will they try to get in your way. In your presence, anyone possessing powers linked to the supernatural lowers their Opposition Level by 1. Your holy aura emits an intense light that can illuminate the whole area around you at your will.","notes":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Invoke holy divine power by reproaching all sinners and providing an example of purity and righteousness."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241692,"modifiedTime":1783973241692,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"KdPxC6sGdnW8CsmL","name":"Dark Ego - Descendant of the Awakening of the Void and the Emptiness","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>cuando liberas tu verdadero poder, tu cuerpo emite una luz divina y nadie puede detenerte. Puedes sufrir 1 Herida adicional para obtener 2 Éxitos adicionales a cualquier prueba física que tengas que realizar. Durante el resto de la escena, los hechizos tienen poco efecto sobre ti y obtienes 2 éxitos adicionales a cualquier prueba de defensa que realices para protegerte de los efectos arcanos. Cuando golpeas a alguien, puedes gastar 1 Soma para infligirle 1 Herida adicional. Los efectos de este don terminan si te comportas de forma serena y obediente, como dicta tu papel de guardián.</p>","trigger":"Actuar con pasión y fuerza, mostrando a todo el mundo el increíble poder que encierra tu cuerpo."},"name":"Ego oscuro - Descendiente del Despertar del Vacío y la Vacuidad"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Associated Descriptor</h3>My essence is magical, and this makes me resistant to enchantments that might snare stupid humans. My spiritual presence is imposing, and I struggle to hide what I am, especially in the eyes of those accustomed to magic.<h3>Dark Ego</h3>When you release your true power, your body emits a divine light and no one can stop you. Take 1 Wound to get 2 Additional Successes to any physical Checks you have to perform. For the rest of the Scene spells have little effect on you and you get 2 Additional Successes to any Defense Check you make to protect yourself from arcane effects. When you deal a hit to someone, you can spend 1 Soma to inflict 1 additional Wound. The effects of this Gift cease if you behave in a composed and obedient manner, as your role as guardian dictates.","notes":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Act with passion and strength, showing everyone the incredible power that lies within your body."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241692,"modifiedTime":1783973241692,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"oHHqcuRoKu5TfEyO","name":"Dark Ego - The Unscrupulous Assassin","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>puedes parecer un caballero civilizado, pero las apariencias engañan. Cuando sea necesario, no dudarás en matar. Si eliminas a un PNJ infligiéndole la Herida final, también puedes eliminar inmediatamente a un segundo PNJ menor. Cuando te defiendes con éxito de una acción violenta, puedes eliminar inmediatamente a un PNJ menor como respuesta. En cualquier caso, el objetivo debe estar dentro del alcance de tu ira. Después de infligir 1 Herida a alguien, puedes moverte libremente como acción adicional, lo que te permite alcanzar a tu verdadero objetivo sin que nadie pueda impedírtelo.</p>","trigger":"revelar su lado oscuro hiriendo a alguien o actuando con agresividad a pesar de tu apariencia exterior tranquila y formal."},"name":"Ego oscuro - El asesino sin escrúpulos"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Associated Descriptor</h3>Under the facade of a respectable man hides a skilled, unscrupulous problem-solver. I know how to kill and how to act with decisiveness. Everyone has done something they are not proud of and I can’t stand seeing the hypocrites who pretend as if they are morally superior to others.<h3>Dark Ego</h3>You may appear as a civilized gentleman, but appearances can be deceiving. When necessary, you will not hesitate to kill. If you eliminate an NPC by inflicting a final Wound, you can also immediately eliminate a second Minor NPC. When you successfully defend yourself from a violent action, you can immediately eliminate a Minor NPC in response. Either way, the target must be within range of your wrath. After inflicting 1 Wound to someone, you can move freely as an additional action, allowing you to reach your true goal without anyone preventing you from doing so.","notes":"Verdoux Bluebeard - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Reveal your dark side by injuring someone or acting aggressively despite your outwardly calm and staid appearance."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241693,"modifiedTime":1783973241693,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"RcU9qkh6Vi8KJPAx","name":"Dark Ego - Ice-Cold","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"system":{"description":"<p>tienes control sobre la temperatura de tu cuerpo y, en consecuencia, puedes congelar el entorno o los objetos que se encuentren a tu alrededor. Cuando manipules hielo, elige un efecto creando un descriptor que lo represente, como por ejemplo: Puerta congelada o Aura de escarcha y gastar 1 Soma para manifestarlo durante toda la Escena. Como efecto adicional, tu escarcha puede infligir 1 Herida a quienes interactúen con ella o hacer que lo que congeles sea increíblemente frágil o increíblemente duro. Quien explote los efectos de la escarcha a su favor obtiene 1 Éxito adicional para su acción. Tu escarcha no tiene efecto directo sobre los seres vivos.</p>","trigger":"deshacerte de tu disfraz de artista sencillo y revelar tu verdadera forma, amargamente fría, o reaccionar con pasión cuando el miedo y la intimidación se utilicen por motivos egoístas."},"name":"Ego oscuro – Fría como el hielo"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Associated Descriptor</h3>My body is pure ice and, because of this, I can manipulate ice as I please. However, I hate to manifest my power because it is dangerous to those around me and, as an artist, my purpose is to make people smile.<h3>Dark Ego</h3>You have control over your body temperature and, consequently, you can freeze the environment or objects in your immediate vicinity. When you manipulate ice, choose an effect by creating a Descriptor that represents it such as: Frozen Door or Aura of Frost and spend 1 Soma to manifest it for the whole Scene. As an additional effect, your frost can inflict 1 Wound on those who interact with it or make what you freeze incredibly fragile or incredibly hard. Whoever exploits the effects of frost in their favor gains 1 Additional Success for their action. Your frost has no direct effect on living things.","notes":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist - bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Shed your disguise as a simple artist and reveal your true, bitterly cold form or react passionately when fear and intimidation are used for selfish reasons."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241693,"modifiedTime":1783973241693,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"D0rGBEuCd9GD1pR1","name":"Dark Ego - The Fox and the Cat","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"translations":{"es":{"system":{},"name":"Ego Oscuro - El Zorro y el Gato"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Associated Descriptor</h3>Like it or not, we are bound by magic. We can share thoughts, each see what the other sees, and thanks to this we can work together to cheat others. Whoever is in animal form hates not being able to communicate and often annoys the other out of spite.<h3>Dark Ego</h3>You and your partner share Soma and Wounds. The human form can spend 1 Soma to use the Gift of the animal form. Once per Scene, if your partner helps you, you gain +2 Additional Successes on a Position Check.","notes":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat - bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Trick or deceive someone, taking advantage of your partner's support."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241693,"modifiedTime":1783973241693,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
